Extending our World With Methods
Next up, we’ll spice up our element class with a few tricks. Just having an elemnet static with no change in electrons is boring and not really chemistry. Let’s first find a way to ionize our electrons and change their charge. To do so, we’ll have to be able to remove electrons from our element and in doing so change the charge. This means we need a way do stuff to our class.

